{"tid":1298961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫壽終正寢？","createTime":"2019-07-09T03:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T03:17:24.000Z","uid":22822,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4e836f8540c5be7af3973de025d1fa2595aba42b","tid":1298961,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"不如我地睇下最多文盲用ga百度點講？<br />\n<br />\n解釋<br />\n科學上講<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人體</span></span>的各部分機能由於老化、組織死亡導致人本體死亡，非疾病、事故等外在原因造成的死亡。<br />\n壽終：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">年紀很大才死</span></span>；正寢：舊式住宅的正房。 原指老死在家裡。 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現比喻事物的滅亡</span></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n出處<br />\n明許仲琳《封神演義》第十一回：你道朕不能善終，你自誇壽終正寢，非侮君而何！<br />\n這樣看來，郵遞這條路是要斷絕了，刊物也就不免壽終正寢了！ &mdash;&mdash;鄒韜奮《患難餘生記&middot;流亡》<br />\n<br />\nSource: 殘體注意<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/寿终正寝\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbaike.baidu.com%2Fitem%2F%E5%AF%BF%E7%BB%88%E6%AD%A3%E5%AF%9D&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0drTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=16df66be\" target=\"_blank\">https://baike.baidu.com/item/寿终正寝</a><br />\n<br />\n文盲都知係比喻黎，咩係比喻？<br />\n姐係唔係法律詞彙，任得佢講。佢今日可以咁詮釋黎個比喻，過番個0月又可以話公眾對黎個比喻ga詮釋有偏差。<br />\n<br />\n唔可以比佢有位走，係徹回，withdrawal。唔係die，唔係pause，更加唔係James Bond"},{"pid":"2cb533b32792539463b87c59be8f7bc26bbfe002","tid":1298961,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"其實政府應該用死於非命，死不瞑目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4b9e56eb49664aa849685ed918174e8db6e8f6","tid":1298961,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fbcf3fc3ee4a8c91946c0f40a32af78fc7a1457","tid":1298961,"uid":247311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxuEhzg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum